tizani Tirana\n*[[Albanian Cup]] (1): [[1996\u201397 Albanian Cup|1996\u201397]]\n\n;Reggina\n*[[Serie A]] Promotion (1): [[2001\u201302 Serie B|2001\u201302]]\n\n===Individual===\n*[[Serie A]] Man of the Match with Cesena (6)\n*[[Serie A]] Team of the Week with Cesena (4): 2010\n*Albanian Footballer of the Year (1): 2005\n*Albanian Fan's Footballer of the Year (3): 2002, 2005, 2007\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{UEFA player|29077}}\n* {{NFT player|34}}\n* {{Soccerway|erjon-bogdani/4334}}\n* [http://www.gazzetta.it/speciali/statistiche/2008_nw/giocatori/54454.shtml Erjon Bogdani] at La Gazzetta {{in lang|it}} {{dead link|date=March 2019}}\n* {{FootballDatabase.eu|2438}}\n* {{ESPN FC|24380<!-- /erjon-bogdani -->}}\n* [http://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=2175 Erjon Bogdani] at EU-football.info\n* [http://www.fshf.org/garat/components/lojtar.php?player_id=226628 Erjon Bogdani] at [[FSHF]].org\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bogdani, Erjon}}\n[[Category:1977 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Albanian Roman Catholics]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Tirana]]\n[[Category:Albanian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:FK Partizani Tirana players]]\n[[Category:Gen\u00e7lerbirli\u011fi S.K. footballers]]\n[[Category:NK Zagreb players]]\n[[Category:Reggina 1914 players]]\n[[Category:U.S. Salernitana 1919 players]]\n[[Category:Hellas Verona F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Robur Siena players]]\n[[Category:A.C. ChievoVerona players]]\n[[Category:A.S. Livorno Calcio players]]\n[[Category:A.C. Cesena players]]\n[[Category:Albanian Superliga players]]\n[[Category:S\u00fcper Lig players]]\n[[Category:Serie A players]]\n[[Category:Serie B players]]\n[[Category:Croatian First Football League players]]\n[[Category:Albania youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Albania under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Albania international footballers]]\n[[Category:Competitors at the 1997 Mediterranean Games]]\n[[Category:Albanian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Albanian expatriate sportspeople in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Albanian expatriate sportspeople in Croatia]]\n[[Category:Albanian expatriate sportspeople in Italy]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Croatia]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Italy]]\n", "name_user": "KingSkyLord", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eClub", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erjon_Bogdani"}
